Examples

=> Check the codes examples in demo project folder

Features   File name (see example here)
--------   ----------
useState     - Counter // to keep updated value when re-render
useEffect    - TitleUpdater // to run the logic base on the dep array

useContext   - ThemedComponent // to pass the value to child directly
1. create context, 2.then provider, 3.wrap the child component 4. use it

useReducer   - Counter1 // to handle same fun with multiple operations, can pass data as well
useCallback  - Counter2 //  todo later, to cache the fun, so when re-render, the fun won't create again


useMemo      - ExpensiveComputation // for performance, caching the return value of a fun
useRef       - UserInput //ref.current (dom element) // directly access the actual dom elements
useLayoutEffect - MeasureDOM // to operate some logic during resizing before seeing in the browser

passProperties - ComposingComponents


